£50,000 in diamonds.

100
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:21,400
Millions, Minister.

101
00:08:21,435 --> 00:08:22,700
Millions, millions.

102
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:25,500
Who's trying
to stop the shipment?

103
