and take over things.

180
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:05,900
Naturally,
I sent for Modesty.

181
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:09,100
She came like a shot
with Willie Garvin.

182
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,300
What a character!

183
00:13:11,335 --> 00:13:13,400
Terrific guy!

184
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:24,200
We must take you
grouse shooting this autumn.

185
