A little present for you,
my son.

186
00:13:30,700 --> 00:13:31,900
For me?

187
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:34,400
It will help you
in your work.

188
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:41,400
Ahh!

189
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:44,400
The most beautiful thing
I've ever seen!

190
